nhc_headline: ...NARDA HOLDING STEADY IN STRENGTH WELL OUT TO SEA...
summary: ...NARDA HOLDING STEADY IN STRENGTH WELL OUT TO SEA... As of 8:00 AM PDT Fri Sep 26 the center of Narda was located near 16.9, -121.9 with movement WNW at 15 mph. The minimum central pressure was 980 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 90 mph.
